animeTitle: The Demon Queen Said I Am Too Strong
otherNames: The female devil said I was too strong, The Demon Queen Said I Am Too Strong, 女魔王说我太强了
synopsis: I only wanted to retire to a quiet life in the countryside, but I accidentally ended up in another world. In the novice village, I unintentionally became a creation-level existence. Even the demon queen who ruled the world was defeated by a dog I raised. Since then, the demon queen has been living in my house, and my adventure in the other world began from there.
